@FintechPlatform.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000
@merchantId = your-merchant-id-here
@paymentId = your-payment-id-here

### Health Check
GET {{FintechPlatform.Api_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Create Merchant
POST {{FintechPlatform.Api_HostAddress}}/api/merchants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Acme Corp",
  "email": "acme@example.com"
}

###

### Get Merchant by ID
GET {{FintechPlatform.Api_HostAddress}}/api/merchants/{{merchantId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get All Active Merchants
GET {{FintechPlatform.Api_HostAddress}}/api/merchants
Accept: application/json

###

### Create Payment
POST {{FintechPlatform.Api_HostAddress}}/api/merchants/{{merchantId}}/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amountInMinorUnits": 10000,
  "currency": "USD",
  "externalReference": "order-12345",
  "description": "Product purchase"
}

###

### Get Payment by ID
GET {{FintechPlatform.Api_HostAddress}}/api/merchants/{{merchantId}}/payments/{{paymentId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Merchant Payments
GET {{FintechPlatform.Api_HostAddress}}/api/merchants/{{merchantId}}/payments
Accept: application/json

###

### Complete Payment
POST {{FintechPlatform.Api_HostAddress}}/api/merchants/{{merchantId}}/payments/{{paymentId}}/complete
Content-Type: application/json

###
